## Troubleshooting

### Failed Reset
```bash
# Check instance status
npx supabase status

# Manual cleanup if needed
.claude/scripts/cleanup-ports.sh

# Retry with verbose logging
/supabase-reset local --verbose
```

### Payload Issues
```bash
# Check payload schema directly
psql "postgresql://postgres:postgres@localhost:54322/postgres" \
  -c "SELECT schema_name FROM information_schema.schemata WHERE schema_name = 'payload';"

# Verify payload tables
psql "postgresql://postgres:postgres@localhost:54322/postgres" \
  -c "SELECT table_name FROM information_schema.tables WHERE table_schema = 'payload';"
```

### Port Conflicts
```bash
# Check what's using ports
lsof -i :54321-54327
lsof -i :55321-55327

# Manual port cleanup
.claude/scripts/cleanup-ports.sh
```

